<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Inquiry Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Inquiry Received</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong><%= user.firstname %> <%= user.lastname %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have received your inquiry and will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <p><%= user.desc %></p>
        <p>We appreciate your interest and will do our best to address your concerns.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> AmoArte.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
